title: [Saewehna Lagoon]
description: Sunlight filters in through the branches of nearby trees on the shoreline, broken into brilliant shafts that illuminate the vivid blue surface of the lagoon.  A few stray flowers float in the water, drifting around aimlessly as the current shifts them to and fro, and the occasional silvery fish nibbles at the underside.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south
location: the environs of the Saewehna Lagoon
